{
  "stem": "19111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "June 1939, I believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] couple of weeks later or so, they gave the entire town of Vilna to the Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the Lithuanians always said that Vilna is their-- their city, belongs to Lithuania, from way back in-- in history.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said that [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Vilnius-- ?] they called it [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Vilnius, ?] actually.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was their capital hundreds of years ago, and all that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they always had a claim on Vilna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the Russians gave them Vilna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Lithuanian army came in and the Russians withdrew only to the outskirts of Vilna.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Lithuanian army came in on bicycles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was really funny to see them come in on bicycles after the Russians came in with their tanks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A little while later, the Russians took over all of Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it was going back and forth like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we lived under the regime of the Lithuanians for awhile, which was not much of a change at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because the Russians took right over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One year.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From-- I believe, till the Germans attacked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was in 1941.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I believe it was June of 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the Germans--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It was a very somber and very frightening time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we heard that the Germans-- actually, we didn't know that the Germans were attacking until we heard the bombs falling on-- on the town.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At night, suddenly, we heard all these explosions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father jumped out of bed and got out to speak to the neighbors and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew that they were-- that the Germans are attacking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- because we saw also the-- some of the Russian soldiers running in our streets.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
